Package: dpca
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Dynamic Principal Component and Factor Analysis
Description: Efficient implementations for the GDFM as
  suggested by Forni, Lippi (2001). This package currently
  covers (multivariate) spectral density estimation, truncated
  eigendecomposition, selection of the number of dynamic factors,
  projection on common component space.
Author: Christoph Rust [aut,cre]
Maintainer: Christoph Rust <christoph.g.rust@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    freqdom (>= 2.0.3)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
